

! 1. SHOW NETWORK TOPOLOGY (on any router)
show cdp neighbors

! 2. SHOW CORE NETWORK (on P1)
show ip ospf neighbor
show ip ospf database
show ip route
ping 2.2.2.2
ping 3.3.3.3

! 3. SHOW MPLS IN CORE (on P2)
show mpls interfaces
show mpls ldp neighbor
show mpls forwarding-table

! 4. SHOW VRFs (on PE1)
show ip vrf
show ip vrf detail CUSTOMER_A
show ip route vrf CUSTOMER_A

! 5. SHOW MP-BGP (on PE2)
show ip bgp vpnv4 all summary
show ip bgp vpnv4 all
show ip bgp vpnv4 vrf CUSTOMER_A

! 6. SHOW MPLS LABELS FOR VPN (on PE3)
show ip bgp vpnv4 all labels
show mpls forwarding-table vrf CUSTOMER_B

! 7. TEST CUSTOMER CONNECTIVITY (on CE1)
ping 192.168.30.1 repeat 3
traceroute 192.168.30.1

! 8. TEST VPN ISOLATION (on CE2)
ping 192.168.10.1
ping 192.168.30.1
